\item In the AC amplifier shown in the figure, $R_S=1.5K\Omega$, $R_1=10K\Omega$, 
$R_2=200K\Omega$, $R_C=3.5K\Omega$, $R_L=2K\Omega$, $\beta=100$, $V_{CC}=20V$.
Also assume $r_{be}=200\Omega$. Find the DC variables $I_B$, $I_C$, $V_C$.

